<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-content {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer-section {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left; /* Center text on mobile */
        }

        .footer-section h4 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer-section p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ccc;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer-section a {
            font-size: 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ccc;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-section a:hover {
            color: #04d39f;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #444;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .footer-bottom p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .footer-bottom p a {
            color: #04d39f;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer-bottom p a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer-section button {
            background-color: #04d39f;
            padding: 10px 20px; /* Increased padding for better touch target */
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            font-size: 14px; /* Adjusted font size */
            margin-top: 10px; /* Added margin for spacing */
        }

        .footer-section input {
            padding: 10px 20px; /* Increased padding for better touch target */
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            font-size: 14px; /* Adjusted font size */
            margin-top: 10px; /* Added margin for spacing */
            width: 100%; /* Full width input on mobile */
        }

        @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
            .footer-content {
                justify-content: space-between; /* Adjust for larger screens */
            }

            .footer-section {
                width: 23%; /* Restore original width */
                text-align: left; /* Adjust alignment */
            }

            .footer-section button,
            .footer-section input {
                width: auto; /* Restore original input/button width */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h4>About Us</h4>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore
                    et dolore magna aliqua.</p>
                <a href="#">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h4>Customer Service</h4>
                <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
                <a href="#">FAQ</a>
                <a href="#">Shipping & Returns</a>
                <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h4>Follow Us</h4>
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Twitter</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h4>Newsletter</h4>
                <p>Subscribe to our newsletter to get the latest updates and offers.</p>
                <form>
                    <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
                    <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; Sundarbans@2024. All Rights Reserved. <a href="#">Terms of Service</a> | <a href="#">Privacy
                    Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
